pull_request.title: documentation consolidation
pull_request.body:
Build instruction & build parameter option documentation was duplicated in different places (this README and the Wiki) leading to duplicate maintenance effort and reader confusion. This PR streamlines this. Also added is some more guidance building for Windows.

* [ ] Does this PR change the input/output behaviour of a cryptographic algorithm (i.e., does it change known answer test values)?  (If so, a version bump will be required from *x.y.z* to *x.(y+1).0*.)
* [ ] Does this PR change the the list of algorithms available -- either adding, removing, or renaming?  (If so, PRs in OQS-OpenSSL, OQS-BoringSSL, and OQS-OpenSSH will also be required by the time this is merged.)

repo.name: liboqs
repo.description: C library for prototyping and experimenting with quantum-resistant cryptography

pull_request.title: Fix missing sha3 symbols for some Windows configurations
pull_request.body: The sha3 CMakeLists.txt file was ignoring the OQS_ENABLE_SHA3_xkcp_low_avx2 option. This option is used to disable our AVX2 implementation of sha3 on Windows. Fixing this resolves one of several problems identified in #997.
